Email and SMS agencies, here’s how to productise your offer: 

Every client’s success roadmap will look slightly different from one another.

So I don’t believe in delivering cookie-cutter services.

However -

The only major differences from client-to-client in terms of service delivery usually boil down to:

- Types of flows
- Types of campaigns

Everything else should be structured the same:

- Onboarding
- Results tracking
- Client check-ins

That said, there are 3 core packages that most retention agencies offer.

1 - Project packages (setting up foundational flows)
2 - Low level retainers (core email/sms deliverables)
3 - High level retainers (core deliverables + advanced strategy)

Boo! Meet the EV Charging GHOST! 

Now I thought I’d seen everything in our ️industry with the hours I spend studying it but, alas, today I was introduced to something I have never seen before and, quite frankly, it looks pretty awesome!

have created a Flattening-Charging solution for electric vehicles! 

Traditional round cables can be tedious, bulky, and hazardous in major cites, a challenge for many urban and suburban environments.

This flat-corded charger is engineered to lay flat, reducing tripping risks and providing a sleek, space-saving solution, rolling up for storage. Whether you're charging at home or on the go, the design offers an alternative EV charging solution that can be safer and more convenient than ever.

The GHOST flat cable is weather-resistant, preventing freezing and stiffening in cold temperatures which makes it unique in their current ability to perform under the toughest conditions.

With the capability to deliver up to 40A and 9.6kW, Ghost provides up to 30 miles of charge per hour.

In Europe and China, their 50A model delivers up to 48 miles per hour, ensuring fast and efficient charging for all EVs. Plus they offer a mode three cable.

Plus, the charger’s low profile meets ADA requirements, making it safe for pedestrians and still offering high performance.

They are also working on a retractable wall charger, and later on an inductive charging pad featuring their flat cable technology.

Clearly they are well positioned to provide a flexible, reliable solution for city dwellers, suburban homeowners, and businesses.

Nice work/ David Sirieix

"Do you think AI will ever replace private bankers like you?" A client jokingly asked me last week..

I smiled and told him to think like that.

Imagine a world where I walk into a meeting armed with insights not just from the last market report but also from real-time, AI-powered analysis.

AI tools have already started predicting market trends with astounding accuracy—up to 90% in some cases for specific asset classes.

Now, combine that with a ‘human touch’: understanding your unique goals, aspirations, and values.

Wouldn’t you be elated?

Another aspect? Automation.

Routine tasks like rebalancing portfolios or generating reports—things that once took hours and used to be done manually—can now be done in minutes. This frees up time for me to do what I love the most: building relationships and strategizing for long-term growth.

AI is an ‘enabler’ to all of us - AI is not just analysing past trends anymore, it's about reacting to your behavior in real-time - quickly & effectively!

And that's where it enables we private bankers to create ‘impact’ in a better way!

The future of private banking isn’t about choosing between AI and humans—it’s about blending the precision of technology with the empathy of human connection.

Private Banking has evolved beyond just market analysis and suggesting a specific product depending upon the client's need! It has become more of ‘𝘤𝘶𝘳𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘰𝘯 𝘰𝘧 𝘧𝘶𝘵𝘶𝘳𝘪𝘴𝘵𝘪𝘤 𝘱𝘰𝘳𝘵𝘧𝘰𝘭𝘪𝘰𝘴’ with a blend of changing market dynamism and the values that need to be adhered!

At the end of the day, private banking is still about trust, relationships, and understanding the human side of wealth creation.

𝘍𝘰𝘳 𝘌𝘹𝘢𝘮𝘱𝘭𝘦 - 𝘞𝘩𝘪𝘤𝘩 𝘈𝘐/𝘋𝘦𝘦𝘱𝘛𝘦𝘤𝘩 𝘴𝘵𝘢𝘳𝘵𝘶𝘱 𝘧𝘳𝘰𝘮 𝘸𝘩𝘪𝘤𝘩 𝘴𝘦𝘤𝘵𝘰𝘳/𝘪𝘯𝘥𝘶𝘴𝘵𝘳𝘺 𝘮𝘦𝘳𝘪𝘵𝘴 𝘢 𝘴𝘵𝘳𝘰𝘯𝘨 𝘢𝘭𝘭𝘰𝘤𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘰𝘯 𝘪𝘯 𝘺𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘱𝘰𝘳𝘵𝘧𝘰𝘭𝘪𝘰 - 𝘪𝘴 𝘸𝘩𝘦𝘳𝘦 𝘸𝘦 ‘𝘱𝘳𝘪𝘷𝘢𝘵𝘦 𝘣𝘢𝘯𝘬𝘦𝘳𝘴’ 𝘣𝘳𝘪𝘯𝘨 ‘𝘪𝘳𝘳𝘦𝘱𝘭𝘢𝘤𝘦𝘢𝘣𝘭𝘦’ 𝘝𝘢𝘭𝘶𝘦!

Moreover, it's NOT just about the ‘human touch’, it's about bringing ‘VISION’ for using new age technologies like AI to create ‘Sustainable Wealth’.

Homeownership remains one of the most significant personal investments because it intertwines financial stability with emotional fulfillment.

Have you ever pondered how the walls of a first home can echo both happiness and cherished family memories?

Beyond its monetary value, a home serves as a canvas where life’s most treasured moments are painted. For those of us in finance and strategic planning, the profound value a home brings reminds us that investments aren't solely about numbers on a ledger—they're about nurturing human experiences.

For first-time buyers, here's a strategic yet heartfelt approach: Prioritize neighborhoods that offer community-building amenities, visualize versatile spaces that adapt with your family's growth, and weigh long-term environmental impact to align your values with your financial commitment.

In an era of fast-paced digital transactions, let’s not forget that some investments, like a home, offer returns in ways financial markets cannot quantify. Choose wisely to not only grow your asset portfolio but to invest in a lifetime of memories.



How does your home investment serve your soul as much as your wallet? Share your thoughts and let's discuss how you’ve turned your house into a cherished home!
